y in the inward-looking nation. It also is unclear whether she has any formal political ambitions, although last week she appeared to be thinking about a future in <LOCATION> Burma </LOCATION>. `` The Burmese people love my father very much and I think they are ready to support me because I'm my father's daughter,'' she said.
