 <PERSON> Martin </PERSON> <PERSON> Weiser </PERSON>, a film publicist who once transformed a <LOCATION> Sunset </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Boulevard </LOCATION> theater into a giant Easter bonnet to promote the opening of `` Mame,'' died Sunday. He was 76.
