<DATELINE>SALT LAKE CITY (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 A former engineer's $ 3 billion lawsuits against rocket-maker <PERSON> Morton </PERSON> <PERSON> Thiokol </PERSON>, stemming from his warnings against launching the ill-fated Challenger space shuttle mission, were dismissed Friday by a judge. <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> District Judge <PERSON> David </PERSON> <PERSON> K. </PERSON> <PERSON> Winder </PERSON>'s decision came after more than six months of deliberations on <ORGANIZATION> Morton </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Thiokol </ORGANIZATION>'s motions to dismiss the suits filed by <PERSON> Roger </PERSON> <PERSON> Boisjoly </PERSON>. Telephone calls to <PERSON> Boisjoly </PERSON>'s <PERSON> Willard </PERSON> residence were answered by a recording. He did not return messages. His attorney, <PERSON> Robert </PERSON> <PERSON> Levin </PERSON>, said from his office in <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> D.C. </LOCATION>, that a decision had not been made on whether to appeal <PERSON> Winder </PERSON>'s ruling to the 10th U.S. <ORGANIZATION> Circuit </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Court </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Appeals </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> Denver </LOCATION>. `` I obviously wish it was better news than we got,'' <PERSON> Levin </PERSON> said. `` -LRB- But -RRB- I have n't seen it yet, and I obviously ca n't comment on a ruling I have n't seen.'' <ORGANIZATION> Morton </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Thiokol </ORGANIZATION> officials were elated, said company spokesman <PERSON> Ed </PERSON> <PERSON> Snow </PERSON>. `` The dismissal of these two suits completely vindicates <PERSON> Morton </PERSON> <PERSON> Thiokol </PERSON>. We are very happy to have this situation behind us,'' he said. In one of his suits, <PERSON> Boisjoly </PERSON> sought $ 1 billion for the deaths of the seven astronauts killed when Challenger exploded on Jan. 28, 1986, and $ 1 million in compensatory damages for <PERSON> Boisjoly </PERSON>'s own health and career. <PERSON> Boisjoly </PERSON> _