withdraw as the specialist in each of the stocks,'' the statement said. An <ORGANIZATION> NYSE </ORGANIZATION> committee that assigns stocks to specialists was accepting applications from other firms that want to make markets in the four stocks and will likely announce its decision next week, Ms. <PERSON> Gamsin </PERSON> said. For Spear, <ORGANIZATION> Leeds </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION>; <PERSON> Kellogg </PERSON>, one of the biggest <ORGANIZATION> NYSE </ORGANIZATION> specialist firms, it was the second reallocation resulting from post-crash inquiries. Previously, the firm surrendered its franchise in <ORGANIZATION> J.P. </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Morgan </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION><ORGANIZATION> ; </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION>'s stock. In addition, the specialist firms <PERSON> Wagner </PERSON>, <ORGANIZATION> Stott </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION><ORGANIZATION> ; </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION>, <ORGANIZATION> M.J. </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Meehan </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION>; Co.. <PERSON> Lawrence </PERSON>, <ORGANIZATION> O'Donnell </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION><ORGANIZATION> ; </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION>, and <ORGANIZATION> LaBranche </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION><ORGANIZATION> ; </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION> have relinquished market-making rights in some stocks since the crash
